import { ImageResponse } from "next/server";

export const runtime = "edge";

const font = fetch(
  new URL(
    "https://use.typekit.net/af/59b013/00000000000000007735a1aa/30/a?primer=7cdcb44be4a7db8877ffa5c0007b8dd865b3bbc383831fe2ea177f62257a9191&fvd=n5&v=3"
  )
).then((res) => res.arrayBuffer());

const boldFont = fetch(
  new URL(
    "https://use.typekit.net/af/a9ccd8/00000000000000007735a1b7/30/a?primer=7cdcb44be4a7db8877ffa5c0007b8dd865b3bbc383831fe2ea177f62257a9191&fvd=n8&v=3"
  )
).then((res) => res.arrayBuffer());

export const size = {
  width: 1200,
  height: 630,
};
export const alt = "Jeferson Mesquita, meu portf√≥lio ";

export const contentType = "image/png";

// Image generation
export default async function Image() {
  const fontData = await font;

  return new ImageResponse(
    (
      // ImageResponse JSX element
      <div
        style={{
          fontSize: 128,
          background: "white",

          display: "flex",

      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
          width={824}
          height={658}
          fill="none"
        >
          <path fill="url(#a)" d="M0 0h824v658H0z" />
          <defs>
            <pattern
              id="a"
              width={1}
              height={1}
              patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
            >
              <use xlinkHref="#b" transform="scale(.00121 .00152)" />

          Jeferson Mesquita

          style={{ fontFamily: "Soleil" }}
        >
          Meu nome √© Jeferson Mesquita, sou desenvolvedor web e mobile, com
          experi√™ncia em desenvolvimento de aplica√ß√µes web e mobile, utilizando
          as tecnologias mais recentes do mercado.
        </div>
      </div>
    ),
    // ImageResponse options
    {
      // For convenience, we can re-use the exported opengraph-image
      // size config to also set the ImageResponse's width and height.
      ...size,
      fonts: [
        {
          name: "BoldSoleil",
          data: boldFontData,
          style: "normal",
        },
        {
          name: "Soleil",
          data: fontData,
          style: "normal",
        },
      ],
    }
  );
}
